data.name: TextBox1.Text
data.value: Tips: You can enable/disable a System, as well as renaming it. Click on "Save Changes" button to apply your modifications. Warning : no changes will be made on Hyperspin folder structure. An entry in purple means that System is in the XML but has not folder in Hyperspin\Databases. An entry in Grey means that folder for System is found, but is not activated in the MainMenu.xml
